/apps/1812950/extras/d15cb3124fba424e5d5e3b203b688a30.webm?t=1711270917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812950/extras/d15cb3124fba424e5d5e3b203b688a30.mp4?t=1711270917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are more types of ragdolls and each ragdoll will have their own set of properties that describe how it interacts with anything in the world. You can make the Ragdoll Follow, Attack each other, simulate battles, or use them to test, usually on death machines that you crafted, to play around with.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812950/extras/38e1762614933652e32b7051e71d023f.avif?t=1711270917\" width=616 height=100 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sandbox mode<br></li><li>Simulation mode<br></li><li>Build anything (Usually death machines)<br></li><li>Massive playground<br></li><li>Drivable Vehicles<br></li><li>Destructible Items<br></li><li>More inventory items<br></li><li>More unique Ragdolls<br></li><li>More Obstacles<br></li><li>Level Creator<br></li><li>Customization: Customize most of the object's Properties, Functions, colors and re-size them to fit your need.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812950/extras/5a4ad64c955107b7644af9cf530f03c9.poster.avif?t=1711270917\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812950/extras/5a4ad64c955107b7644af9cf530f03c9.webm?t=1711270917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1812950/extras/5a4ad64c955107b7644af9cf530f03c9.mp4?t=1711270917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
